// Tutorial 1 — Your first note
//
// Every BPscript file needs:
//   @core           — core library
//   @controls       — control definitions (vel, chan...)
//   @alphabet.western:browser — which notes to use
//
// Then write a rule: S -> followed by notes.
// S is the start symbol. The engine rewrites S into the notes.
//
// Try: click Produce, then Play.

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser

S -> C4
